        <span class="about-story-imgframe"><img src="{{ 'about-6.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="The River Thames and the London skyline at blue hour"></span>
        <figcaption class="about-story-caption">Made properly, or not at all</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <div class="about-story-text reveal">
        <span class="about-chapter-num">05</span>
        <span class="section-label">The standard</span>
        <h2>Made properly, or not at all</h2>
        <p>To make mirrors properly, we went looking for people who still cared about making things properly. We spoke with manufacturers across the world and chose only those who could meet our standard.</p>
        <p>Premium stainless steel, ecological silver glass that is copper free and lead free, and a level of finish you can feel. Two things are never for sale here: quality and responsibility.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

